
How to use:
1) Import the code from birthday_reminder_program
2) Input your data in the text file ( data: List of birthdays in the format monthDay Fname Lname)
3) In the code, replace the file url with your text file.
4) Run and Enjoy :)



*NOTE*
This program is for ubuntu users.
For windows user find an equivalent system toast message method, and replace it where in the code, this is written:-

os.system('notify-send "Message" ')
